{
  "texts": [
    "We use Zotero (https://www.zotero.org/) to identify and remove 52 duplicate papers.",
    "In addition, 10 papers were excluded based on manual screening for duplication.",
    "105 papers were excluded for various reasons, e.g.",
    "language restriction, publication date, journal type, missing citation, etc.",
    "This resulted in a pool of 277 papers for further evaluation."
  ]
}